3.1.7 Using a Passphrase
prevent unauthorized access to your devices, you should consider using passphrases instead of passwords.
passphrase generally takes the form of a sentence (‘Acat th@tlov3sd0gs.’),

Choose a statement that is meaningful to you. 
Add special characters such as ! @ # $ % ^ & * ( )
The longer the better.
AVOID commonm or famous statements, for example, lyrics from a popular song.
